headline: Jacobs Selected to Design Transformative Water Infrastructure Program for Metro Vancouver
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J), operating under a joint venture with AECOM, was selected to design Metro Vancouver's multi-year program to upgrade the Iona Island Wastewater Treatment Plant. One of Canada's most transformative programs, upgrading and expanding the current treatment plant will enhance water quality allowing the plant to serve nearly one million people by 2051.
